<text><body>
<cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">詩</cb:mulu><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">題石壁山紹上人觀風亭</cb:mulu><cb:div type="other">
<milestone unit="juan" n="46"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0933c03"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0933c04"/><lb ed="R101" n="0187b13"/><cb:juan fun="open" n="46"><cb:mulu type="卷" n="46"></cb:mulu><cb:jhead>閑居編第四十六</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="X" n="0933c05"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0933c06"/><lb ed="R101" n="0187b14"/><byline cb:type="author">宋孤山沙門　智圓　著</byline>
<lb ed="X" n="0933c07"/><lb ed="R101" n="0187b15"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">昭君辭</cb:mulu><head>昭君辭</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0933c08"/><lb ed="R101" n="0187b16"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0933c0801"><l>昭君停車淚暫止<caesura/>為把功名奏天子</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0933c09"/><lb ed="R101" n="0187b17"/><l>靜得胡塵唯妾身<caesura/>漢家文武合羞死</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0933c10"/><lb ed="R101" n="0187b18"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">老將</cb:mulu><head>老將</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0933c11"/><lb ed="R101" n="0188a01"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0933c1101"><l>畫堂升降子孫扶<caesura/>白髮<g ref="#CB02575"/><g ref="#CB02575"/>膽尚麤</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0933c12"/><lb ed="R101" n="0188a02"/><l>不省時清身<note n="0933c1201" resp="CBETA" type="add">已【CB】，巳【卍續】</note><app n="0933c1201"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">已</lem><rdg wit="【卍續】">巳</rdg></app>老<caesura/>逢人猶說斬單于</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0933c13"/><lb ed="R101" n="0188a03"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">邊將二首</cb:mulu><head>邊將二首</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0933c14"/><lb ed="R101" n="0188a04"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0933c1401"><l>威聲飛將豈能過<caesura/>號令雄師劒始磨</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0933c15"/><lb ed="R101" n="0188a05"/><l>雪攪長空馬殭立<caesura/>偷營今夜度膠河</l></lg>
<lb ed="X" n="0933c16"/><lb ed="R101" n="0188a06"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">其一</cb:mulu><head>其一</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0933c17"/><lb ed="R101" n="0188a07"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0933c1701"><l>百戰依前勇氣成<caesura/>窮邊深入耀精兵</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0933c18"/><lb ed="R101" n="0188a08"/><l>穹廬燒盡龍庭破<caesura/>却上燕然更勒銘</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0933c19"/><lb ed="R101" n="0188a09"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">其二</cb:mulu><head>其二</head></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0933c20"/><lb ed="R101" n="0188a10"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">貪泉</cb:mulu><head>貪泉</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0933c21"/><lb ed="R101" n="0188a11"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0933c2101"><l>隱之曾飲肯為非<caesura/>今古泓澄照翠微</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0933c22"/><lb ed="R101" n="0188a12"/><l>自是貪夫性貪賄<caesura/>便將泉水作因依</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0933c23"/><lb ed="R101" n="0188a13"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">夷齊廟</cb:mulu><head>夷齊廟</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0933c24"/><lb ed="R101" n="0188a14"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0933c2401"><l>曾聞叩馬犯君顏<caesura/>萬古清風滿世間</l>
<pb ed="X" xml:id="X56.0949.0934a" n="0934a"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0934a01"/><lb ed="R101" n="0188a15"/><l>若使干戈為揖讓<caesura/>夷齊終不死空山</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0934a02"/><lb ed="R101" n="0188a16"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">嚴光臺</cb:mulu><head>嚴光臺</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0934a03"/><lb ed="R101" n="0188a17"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0934a0301"><l>撥亂方爭汗馬功<caesura/>賢才誰肯守窮空</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0934a04"/><lb ed="R101" n="0188a18"/><l>嚴光亦是夷齊類<caesura/>埀釣碧溪敦讓風</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0934a05"/><lb ed="R101" n="0188b01"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">閑田</cb:mulu><head>閑田</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0934a06"/><lb ed="R101" n="0188b02"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0934a0601"><l>虞芮懷慚觀禮讓<caesura/>閑田從此草長生</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0934a07"/><lb ed="R101" n="0188b03"/><l>而今雖是文王化<caesura/>難遣貪夫兩不爭</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0934a08"/><lb ed="R101" n="0188b04"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">讀王通中說</cb:mulu><head>讀王通中說</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0934a09"/><lb ed="R101" n="0188b05"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0934a0901"><l>孟軻荀況與楊雄<caesura/>代異言殊道一同</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0934a10"/><lb ed="R101" n="0188b06"/><l>夫子文章天未喪<caesura/>又於隋世產王通</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0934a11"/><lb ed="R101" n="0188b07"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">讀毛詩</cb:mulu><head>讀毛詩</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0934a12"/><lb ed="R101" n="0188b08"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0934a1201"><l>夫子刪來三百章<caesura/>箴規明白佐時王</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0934a13"/><lb ed="R101" n="0188b09"/><l>近來吟詠唯風月<caesura/>謗木詩官事久亡</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0934a14"/><lb ed="R101" n="0188b10"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">讀孫郃集</cb:mulu><head>讀孫郃集</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0934a15"/><lb ed="R101" n="0188b11"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0934a1501"><l>唐祚將亡王澤枯<caesura/>四明歸隱泣窮塗</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0934a16"/><lb ed="R101" n="0188b12"/><l>而今若撰才名志<caesura/>更有閑僧得入無</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0934a17"/><lb ed="R101" n="0188b13"/><l><note place="inline">郃撰四明才名志釋宗亮預焉</note></l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0934a18"/><lb ed="R101" n="0188b14"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">讀禪月集</cb:mulu><head>讀禪月集</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0934a19"/><lb ed="R101" n="0188b15"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0934a1901"><l>屬興難忘水與山<caesura/>救時箴戒出其間</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0934a20"/><lb ed="R101" n="0188b16"/><l>讀終翻恨吾生<g ref="#CB15085"/><caesura/>不得斯人一往還</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0934a21"/><lb ed="R101" n="0188b17"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">觀劒客圖</cb:mulu><head>觀劒客圖</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0934a22"/><lb ed="R101" n="0188b18"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0934a2201"><l>飛劒縱橫乍可驚<caesura/>翻疑風俗妄傳聲</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0934a23"/><lb ed="R101" n="0189a01"/><l>如今至究在何處<caesura/>不出為人平不平</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0934a24"/><lb ed="R101" n="0189a02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">詩魔</cb:mulu><head>詩魔</head>
<pb ed="X" xml:id="X56.0949.0934b" n="0934b"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0934b01"/><lb ed="R101" n="0189a03"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0934b0101"><l>禪心喧撓被詩魔<caesura/>月冷風清柰爾何</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0934b02"/><lb ed="R101" n="0189a04"/><l>一夜欲降降不得<caesura/>紛紛徒屬更來多</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0934b03"/><lb ed="R101" n="0189a05"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">謝僧惠蒲扇</cb:mulu><head>謝僧惠蒲扇</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0934b04"/><lb ed="R101" n="0189a06"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0934b0401"><l>結蒲為扇狀何奇<caesura/>助我淳風世罕知</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0934b05"/><lb ed="R101" n="0189a07"/><l>林下靜搖來客笑<caesura/>竹牀茆屋恰相宜</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0934b06"/><lb ed="R101" n="0189a08"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">招元羽律師</cb:mulu><head>招元羽律師</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0934b07"/><lb ed="R101" n="0189a09"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0934b0701"><l>去年相訪宿吾廬<caesura/>露滴蒼苔夜話遲</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0934b08"/><lb ed="R101" n="0189a10"/><l>湖水<g ref="#CB15085"/>來清不極<caesura/>今秋又是月圓時</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0934b09"/><lb ed="R101" n="0189a11"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">貧居</cb:mulu><head>貧居</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0934b10"/><lb ed="R101" n="0189a12"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0934b1001"><l>山厨竈上苔痕碧<caesura/>齋盂生塵無粒食</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0934b11"/><lb ed="R101" n="0189a13"/><l>可憐<g ref="#CB15179"/>鼠未知貧<caesura/>穿屋穿墉不暫息</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0934b12"/><lb ed="R101" n="0189a14"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">詶簡上人見寄</cb:mulu><head>詶簡上人見寄</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0934b13"/><lb ed="R101" n="0189a15"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0934b1301"><l>林間病臥懶逢迎<caesura/>相識何人最愜情</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0934b14"/><lb ed="R101" n="0189a16"/><l>唯有簡公閑且僻<caesura/>寂寥翻被俗流輕</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0934b15"/><lb ed="R101" n="0189a17"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">送僧歸姑蘇</cb:mulu><head>送僧歸姑蘇</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0934b16"/><lb ed="R101" n="0189a18"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0934b1601"><l>姑蘇臺畔樹含秋<caesura/>蟬噪西風雨乍收</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0934b17"/><lb ed="R101" n="0189b01"/><l>閑笑閑吟忽歸去<caesura/>月明何處宿孤舟</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0934b18"/><lb ed="R101" n="0189b02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">寄遠</cb:mulu><head>寄遠</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0934b19"/><lb ed="R101" n="0189b03"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0934b1901"><l>洞房秋<g ref="#CB15085"/>更思君<caesura/>寶瑟慵彈日又曛</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0934b20"/><lb ed="R101" n="0189b04"/><l>鴈過長空書不到<caesura/>滿庭黃葉落紛紛</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0934b21"/><lb ed="R101" n="0189b05"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">謝仁上人惠茶</cb:mulu><head>謝仁上人惠茶</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0934b22"/><lb ed="R101" n="0189b06"/><lg xml:id="lgX56p0934b2201"><l>寄我山茶號雨前<caesura/>齋餘閑試僕夫泉</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0934b23"/><lb ed="R101" n="0189b07"/><l><note place="inline">予止山居有之</note></l>
<lb ed="X" n="0934b24"/><lb ed="R101" n="0189b08"/><l>睡魔遣得雖相感<caesura/>翻引詩魔來眼前</l></lg></cb:div>
<pb ed="X" xml:id="X56.0949.0934c" n="0934c"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0934c01"/><lb ed="R101" n="0189b09"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">讀項羽傳二首</cb:mulu><head>讀項羽傳二首</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0934c02"/><lb ed="R101" n="0189b10"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0934c0201"><l>頻年戰勝恃雄強<caesura/>歷數分明在彼蒼</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0934c03"/><lb ed="R101" n="0189b11"/><l>堪笑范曾無異識<caesura/>不能令主事高皇</l></lg>
<lb ed="X" n="0934c04"/><lb ed="R101" n="0189b12"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">其一</cb:mulu><head>其一</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0934c05"/><lb ed="R101" n="0189b13"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0934c0501"><l>發歎虞姬勢<note n="0934c0501" resp="CBETA" type="add">已【CB】，巳【卍續】</note><app n="0934c0501"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">已</lem><rdg wit="【卍續】">巳</rdg></app>窮<caesura/>烏江此夕喪英雄</l>
